  <entry>
    <base>GIT_PRIVILEGES_NOTE</base>
    <trans>
      <![CDATA[ <p> Use the selection boxes below to you configure the pull and push permissions for the Git repository.<br />
      Select either groups or individual users. Press the SHIFT key to select multiple groups or users.<br />
      If you set neither a group or user setting, the repositoty will be accessible anonymously (i.e. no user name or password will be required).<br />
      If you specify users or groups for pull permissions, the push users will also have pull access.<br />
      If you want your user(s) or group(s) to have exclusive full pull and push access specify them in both the pull and push box.</p> ]]>
    </trans>
